snippet.title: Seaman 2 Gameplay (Sequel to Seaman on Dreamcast)
snippet.description: This is gameplay from 'Seaman 2' -sequel to the cult classic 'Seaman'. For some reason this release for the PS2 is much lesser known although it was only released in Japan.
